{"id": "1496450944760807485", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "author_id": "1326878892664815632", "author_name": "tianfang5580", "content": "Hello, all Morimens! We have a new pvp competition——the 4th 「N」′s chef cup. We welcome all of you to participate. Our principle is that winning or losing is not important; having fun is the most crucial thing. Therefore, our competition has no entry requirements and offers a variety of prizes. Even if you don't achieve a high ranking, you still have a chance to trigger conditional prizes. If your operation makes people burst into laughter, you will also receive a small amount of prize money and be included in our pvp competitions' \"monument\". The most popular player will have the opportunity to win a large sum of money and be included in the top layer of the \"monument\". Of course, for phase masters, we also have corresponding first, second, and third place prizes. Meanwhile, the top four players will have the chance to receive a limited in-game avatar frame. Whether you are a phase novice or a master, everyone is welcome to sign up. Click the link below to fill out the registration form to sign up. The competition system and detailed prize information are shown in the picture below. The registration period is from May 1st to May 15th. After successful registration, a member of the event team will contact you. We also welcome all friends to come and watch the competition. We will be live streaming on both Bilibili and DC voice channels. The competition and live streaming time will be from May 22nd, every Friday, Saturday, and Sunday from 7 p.m. to 10 p.m. (UTC+8) [Tencent Document] 4th 「N」's Chef Cup Registration Form https://docs.qq.com/form/page/DSnp6ZnBTU0R1cE1N\n【Tencent Document】PVP Tournament Monument https://docs.qq.com/sheet/DSkxsYm5ydW5UQ0Vx", "timestamp": "2026-04-22T10:01:47.945000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1496450946039812146", "filename": "Image_1776840337349_80.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1377269, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1326453691527594035/1496450946039812146/Image_1776840337349_80.png?ex=69e9ee0c&is=69e89c8c&hm=2a8566846ed82ee63c62c43eb6fc3e5b67652b0423dba61187a1a489e1c7363e&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "link", "title": "第四届N厨杯报名表", "url": "https://docs.qq.com/form/page/DSnp6ZnBTU0R1cE1N", "description": "腾讯文档-在线收集表"}, {"type": "link", "title": "pvp赛事名人唐", "url": "https://docs.qq.com/sheet/DSkxsYm5ydW5UQ0Vx", "description": "腾讯文档-在线表格"}]}
